  "dialogues": [
    {
      "id": "dlg_old_beggar_first",
      "name": "老乞丐初次对话",
      "relatedNpc": "old_beggar",
      "startNode": "node_01",
      "nodes": {
        "node_01": {
          "id": "node_01",
          "speaker": "old_beggar",
          "expression": "squint",
          "text": "这位少侠，一看就是初来乍到吧？老叫花子在洛阳待了三十年，这城里的事，没有我不知道的。",
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "c1",
              "text": "（恭敬行礼）老前辈，晚辈初到洛阳，想打听一些消息。",
              "effects": {
                "affinityChange": 5
              },
              "nextNode": "node_02a"
            },
            {
              "id": "c2",
              "text": "（扔下几枚铜钱）说吧，你知道些什么？",
              "effects": {
                "affinityChange": -3
              },
              "nextNode": "node_02b"
            },
            {
              "id": "c3",
              "text": "一个乞丐能知道什么？别浪费我时间。",
              "effects": {
                "affinityChange": -20
              },
              "nextNode": "node_02c"
            }
          ]
        },
        "node_02a": {
          "id": "node_02a",
          "speaker": "old_beggar",
          "expression": "pleased",
          "text": "哈哈哈，难得有人对老叫花子这么客气。你想打听什么？江湖大事，还是洛阳城的犄角旮旯？",
          "nextNode": "node_03"
        },
        "node_02b": {
          "id": "node_02b",
          "speaker": "old_beggar",
          "expression": "neutral",
          "text": "铜钱虽少，也是一番心意。老叫花子就告诉你吧——最近城外山贼闹得厉害，官府正在招募人手。",
          "effects": {
            "startQuest": "main_ch1_02"
          },
          "nextNode": "node_end"
        },
        "node_02c": {
          "id": "node_02c",
          "speaker": "old_beggar",
          "expression": "angry",
          "text": "哼，狗眼看人低！老叫花子虽然衣衫褴褛，却也曾是江湖上响当当的人物。你这种人，不配听我说话！",
          "nextNode": "node_end"
        },
        "node_03": {
          "id": "node_03",
          "speaker": "old_beggar",
          "expression": "serious",
          "text": "说到大事……少侠，你腰间那块玉佩，可否让老叫花子看看？",
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "c4",
              "text": "（递过玉佩）前辈认得此物？",
              "nextNode": "node_04"
            },
            {
              "id": "c5",
              "text": "（警惕地收回玉佩）这是我的私人物品。",
              "effects": {
                "affinityChange": -10
              },
              "nextNode": "node_end"
            }
          ]
        },
        "node_04": {
          "id": "node_04",
          "speaker": "old_beggar",
          "expression": "shocked",
          "text": "这……这是「七星佩」！没想到老叫花子有生之年还能再见到它。少侠，你这玉佩从何而来？",
          "effects": {
            "setFlag": "jade_identified"
          },
          "nextNode": "node_end"
        },
        "node_end": {
          "id": "node_end",
          "speaker": "system",
          "text": "（对话结束）"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "dlg_guard_intro",
      "name": "守卫对话",
      "relatedNpc": "village_guard",
      "startNode": "node_01",
      "nodes": {
        "node_01": {
          "id": "node_01",
          "speaker": "village_guard",
          "expression": "neutral",
          "text": "这里是新手村，往东走就是洛阳城了。不过最近城外山贼闹得厉害，少侠若是要出村，最好准备充分一些。",
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "c1",
              "text": "多谢提醒，我会小心的。",
              "nextNode": "node_02"
            },
            {
              "id": "c2",
              "text": "山贼？他们有多少人？",
              "nextNode": "node_03"
            }
          ]
        },
        "node_02": {
          "id": "node_02",
          "speaker": "village_guard",
          "text": "嗯，看你也是个练家子。村里的杂货铺和药铺都有补给，不妨去逛逛。",
          "nextNode": "node_end"
        },
        "node_03": {
          "id": "node_03",
          "speaker": "village_guard",
          "text": "少说也有二三十人，盘踞在郊外的山寨里。听说张捕头正在招募人手剿匪，少侠有兴趣可以去衙门看看。",
          "effects": {
            "startQuest": "main_ch1_02"
          },
          "nextNode": "node_end"
        },
        "node_end": {
          "id": "node_end",
          "speaker": "system",
          "text": "（对话结束）"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "dlg_teahouse_gossip",
      "name": "茶馆闲聊",
      "relatedNpc": "teahouse_owner",
      "startNode": "node_01",
      "nodes": {
        "node_01": {
          "id": "node_01",
          "speaker": "teahouse_owner",
          "expression": "friendly",
          "text": "客官来啦！喝茶还是听说书？咱们这儿有上好的龙井，还有新鲜出炉的江湖八卦。",
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "c1",
              "text": "来壶龙井，顺便听听最近有什么新鲜事。",
              "nextNode": "node_02a"
            },
            {
              "id": "c2",
              "text": "不用了，我随便看看。",
              "nextNode": "node_end"
            }
          ]
        },
        "node_02a": {
          "id": "node_02a",
          "speaker": "teahouse_owner",
          "text": "嘿，最近最大的新闻就是少林寺藏经阁丢了本经书。方丈气得不行，正四处找线索呢。还有就是，听说城外山贼绑架了个老道士，那老道嘴里一直念叨什么「七星佩」……",
          "nextNode": "node_end"
        },
        "node_end": {
          "id": "node_end",
          "speaker": "system",
          "text": "（对话结束）"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "dlg_wushi",
      "relatedNpc": "wushi",
      "startNode": "node_01",
      "nodes": {
        "node_01": {
          "id": "node_01",
          "speaker": "wushi",
          "expression": "stern",
          "text": "年轻人，我看你骨骼清奇，是个练武的好苗子。老夫在此隐居多年，也算是缘分。这江湖险恶，你既要闯荡，须得先练好基本功。",
          "nextNode": "node_02"
        },
        "node_02": {
          "id": "node_02",
          "speaker": "wushi",
          "expression": "neutral",
          "text": "山贼和野狼常在附近出没，正是你磨炼身手的好靶子。另外，这山里草药不少，采些回来或许能救你一命。若有余钱，去李货郎的杂货铺看看，买些丹药防身。",
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "c1",
              "text": "晚辈明白，这就去练练手。",
              "nextNode": "node_accept"
            },
            {
              "id": "c2",
              "text": "多谢前辈指点。",
              "nextNode": "node_end"
            }
          ]
        },
        "node_accept": {
          "id": "node_accept",
          "speaker": "wushi",
          "text": "去吧，打赢了就回来，老夫有东西给你。",
          "nextNode": "node_end",
          "acceptQuest": "side_guide_01"
        },
        "node_end": {
          "id": "node_end",
          "speaker": "system",
          "text": "（对话结束）"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "dlg_hermit",
      "name": "采药老人",
      "relatedNpc": "hermit",
      "startNode": "node_01",
      "nodes": {
        "node_01": {
          "id": "node_01",
          "speaker": "hermit",
          "expression": "friendly",
          "text": "哦，一个生面孔。老夫在这片山林采了三十年药，还是头一回见到你这样骨骼清奇的年轻人。",
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "c1",
              "text": "老前辈，这附近有什么要注意的吗？",
              "nextNode": "node_02"
            },
            {
              "id": "c2",
              "text": "我只是路过，不打扰了。",
              "nextNode": "node_end"
            }
          ]
        },
        "node_02": {
          "id": "node_02",
          "speaker": "hermit",
          "expression": "serious",
          "text": "往深处走有山贼出没，不过林子里止血草和聚气草不少，采些回去有大用。你若见到山贼探子，替我教训教训他们——这些家伙踩坏了我不少药田！",
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "c3",
              "text": "好，我若遇到山贼定不轻饶。",
              "effects": {
                "startQuest": "side_hermit_01"
              },
              "nextNode": "node_03"
            },
            {
              "id": "c4",
              "text": "这可不关我的事。",
              "nextNode": "node_end"
            }
          ]
        },
        "node_03": {
          "id": "node_03",
          "speaker": "hermit",
          "expression": "pleased",
          "text": "好小子，有侠义心肠！老夫也不会亏待你。",
          "nextNode": "node_end"
        },
        "node_end": {
          "id": "node_end",
          "speaker": "system",
          "text": "（对话结束）"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "dlg_bandit_scout",
      "name": "山贼探子",
      "relatedNpc": "bandit_scout",
      "startNode": "node_01",
      "nodes": {
        "node_01": {
          "id": "node_01",
          "speaker": "bandit_scout",
          "expression": "angry",
          "text": "站住！你是官府派来的人？还是哪个不长眼的想来送死？",
          "choices": [
            {
              "id": "c1",
              "text": "（拔剑）我是来收拾你们的！",
              "effects": {
                "triggerBattle": {
                  "enemies": [
                    {"name": "山贼", "level": 2, "str": 6, "agi": 4, "con": 5, "int": 2, "wil": 2, "lck": 1, "skills": ["basic_stab"], "count": 2}
                  ]
                }
              },
              "nextNode": "node_fight"
            },
            {
              "id": "c2",
              "text": "我只是路过采药的。",
              "nextNode": "node_02"
            }
          ]
        },
        "node_02": {
          "id": "node_02",
          "speaker": "bandit_scout",
          "expression": "neutral",
          "text": "采药？哼，这山头的药都是我们寨主的。识相的快滚，不然别怪我不客气！",
          "nextNode": "node_end"
        },
        "node_fight": {
          "id": "node_fight",
          "speaker": "bandit_scout",
          "expression": "angry",
          "text": "狂妄！兄弟们，给我上！",
          "nextNode": "node_end"
        },
        "node_end": {
          "id": "node_end",
          "speaker": "system",
          "text": "（对话结束）"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "dlg_bandit_boss",
      "name": "山贼头目",
      "relatedNpc": "bandit_boss",
      "startNode": "node_01",
      "nodes": {
        "node_01": {
          "id": "node_01",
